reviewText: loved the quality and the movie, i reccommend it very so. you will enjoy! get it now before their gone!

I was escatic when I saw this as a combo pack !  I was just looking for "She's All That" after seeing it on television and being reminded how much I adore that movie.  I only saw "Crazy/Beautiful" one time, and I remember being kind of annoyed by Kirsten Dunst in it.  But after watching it again, it is a good movie.  Fabulous package deal !

i haven't seen the movie 'shes all that' in a while
but i remember seeing it when i was like 10, and i really loved it
ive been looking for it everywhere, so in the end i just bought it of here
if you like teen romance movies, then i suggest you buy this movie (:
One of my favorite movie. Just love them both
Movie was good and in good condition!
Every happy that I received my item
Originally was looking for only one of the two movies on this double feature.  Great price.  Received before estimated date and in great condition.

Bought this on Aug 2...Today Nov 10th would have been my first day watching either movie, but instead my screen pops up a disc error...looking at the bottom of the disc I could actually only see where the disc is damaged if in natural lighting...

Two good movies for the prize of one ill take it. I absolutely love these two movies. Crazy/Beautiful great because it tell the story of two people from different parts of town that find each other and love. She's All That is just a good old teen movie that I can't never get enough of; boy helps girl become popular. buy buy buy buy BUY NOW
It was great to get two movies in one. These are both chick flicks that are not too bad. Go a little crazy for a night in.
